description: Condor Ferries said demand had fallen as isolation requirements increased.
title: Poole-Channel Islands sailings cancelled
title_page: Poole-Channel Islands sailings cancelled - BBC News
maintext: He said: "We are mindful that the festive period is not long away so we will be running a service from Poole on 4 December to ensure students at UK universities and college can return home to their families at such an important time.
